# Routing: Standalone + Lazy

- Use lazy route components with `loadComponent`.
- Prefer default export route arrays with `satisfies Routes`.
- Avoid eager `component:` route declarations in feature route files.
- Keep route files focused on routing only (no page logic).

## Example

- ✅ `export default [{ path: '', loadComponent: ... }] satisfies Routes;`
- ❌ `export const routes: Routes = [{ path: '', component: ListPage }];`
